item.title: Madhya Pradesh: 205 women, 16 kids undergo check-up at health camp in Khargone
item.description: Madhya Pradesh: 205 women, 16 kids undergo check-up at health camp in Khargone Khargone (Madhya Pradesh): To deal with the challenge of malnutrition in the region, health camps are being organised across the district.

item.title: Madhya Pradesh: 66th MP State level boxing competition concludes in Guna
item.description: Madhya Pradesh: 66th MP State level boxing competition concludes in Guna Guna (Madhya Pradesh): With spectacular performances and intriguing competitions, 66th State level boxing competition concluded with cultural performances of the students of CM Rise School, Guna on Saturday.

item.title: Madhya Pradesh: CM Rise Badnawar students prove mettle in athletics competition
item.description: Madhya Pradesh: CM Rise Badnawar students prove mettle in athletics competition Badnawar (Madhya Pradesh): Students of CM Rise Excellence School brought laurels to the school by registering a remarkable win at the divisional-level athletics competition which was held at Malhar Ashram, Indore.

item.title: Mhow: 'Birsa Munda akin to God for soldiers of Bihar regiment'
item.description: Mhow: ‘Birsa Munda akin to God for soldiers of Bihar regiment’ Mhow (Madhya Pradesh): The entire life of Dharti Aaba, the helmsman of tribal culture and heritage, has been dedicated to the nation.

item.title: Dewas: Collector Rishav Gupta reviews health department programmes
item.description: Dewas: Collector Rishav Gupta reviews health department programmes Dewas (Madhya Pradesh): The collector of Dewas, Rishav Gupta reviewed various health programmes run by the health department in the collectorate's office hall.
